des:
With Punta Cana Guide skill you can learn of the best restaurants in the area and ask Alexa for recommended not to miss excursions!.

If you are planning on going to the #1 destination on the caribbean then this skill can help you plan your holiday in advance, just ask Alexa for breakfast, lunch or activities and Alexa will recommend and send to your Alexa app!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
